## ğŸ‡®ğŸ‡© Indonesia

**Crisis Resources:**

**Note:** Indonesia has limited centralized suicide prevention hotlines.

**Indonesian Psychological Healthcare Center**
- **Website:** indopsycare.com
- **Services:** English and Indonesian psychotherapy (in-person and online)
- **Locations:** Jakarta (Indonesia Stock Exchange, Menara BCA)

**Emergency Services:**
- **Phone:** 119 (ambulance/medical emergency)
- **Services:** Request psychiatric emergency services

**Mental Health Hospitals:**

**RS Jiwa Dr. Soeharto Heerdjan (Jakarta)**
- **Phone:** (021) 5682841
- **Address:** Jl. Prof. Dr. Latumeten No.1, Jakarta Barat

**Moderator Note:** For Indonesian members in crisis, recommend visiting the nearest emergency center and requesting constant monitoring. Online therapy platforms are increasingly available.

